review_blob: A most enjoyable and easy to dring drop.  Low alcohol but very intense flavour.  Clean and refreshing.  The only hand pumped real ale in Christchurch.
Abominable.  The taste of chemicals is overbearing.  Harsh and nasty.  No wonder it is served at a temperature low enough to avoid having to taste this carbonated wees.
A truly disguisting sap.  The piss of Johnny Howard- no substance, poor taste, foul presentation and no character.
Such an intensely tasty beer, only 3.7%.  Refreshing and crisp.  Beautiful floral aroma.  A real treat!
